# endDate

**Instance Property**

The end time for the pedometer data.

## Declaration

```swift
var endDate: Date { get }
```

## Discussion

The [doc://com.apple.coremotion/documentation/CoreMotion/CMPedometerData/startDate] and `endDate` represent the period of time over which the pedometer data was gathered.

## Getting the Dates

- **startDate**: The start time for the pedometer data.
